321
00:27:59,890 --> 00:28:03,110
Ak sa niečo stane, ihneď zavolaj Taek Baeovi...

322
00:28:03,110 --> 00:28:05,110
- Tu je jeho číslo.
- A čo ty?

323
00:28:05,110 --> 00:28:06,830
Som v pohode.

324
00:28:06,830 --> 00:28:09,860
Mala by si mu zavolať, ak sa niečo stane, dobre?

325
00:28:09,860 --> 00:28:11,570
Dobre.

326
00:28:11,570 --> 00:28:12,860
Uvidíme sa.

327
00:28:31,910 --> 00:28:34,780
Čo to robíš?

328
00:28:53,630 --> 00:28:56,500
Ako mohol nájsť toto miesto?

329
00:28:56,500 --> 00:28:58,900
Dostal oznámenie o smrti tvojej matky.

330
00:28:58,910 --> 00:29:01,400
A z neho získal adresu.

331
00:29:01,400 --> 00:29:02,920
Ako si vedel o tomto mieste?

332
00:29:02,920 --> 00:29:04,920
Odvtedy, ako som sa dostal von z väzenia,

333
00:29:04,920 --> 00:29:06,920
